---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="carles.sh | About"
  description="About Carles Sánchez, Informatics Engineering student and AI researcher at GREIA."
>
  <main class="page-main about-page">
    <section class="window profile-window" aria-labelledby="about-title">
      <div class="window-title"><strong class="window-label">Profile room</strong><small>about Carles</small></div>
      <div class="profile-body">
        <div class="profile-copy">
          <p class="small-label">Hello from Lleida</p>
          <h1 id="about-title">I'm Carles Sánchez.</h1>
          <p class="intro">I am completing a Master's in Informatics Engineering and contributing to AI research at <a href="https://greia.udl.cat/">GREIA</a>.</p>
          <p>I like software that makes difficult problems easier to inspect: data pipelines, model experiments, low-level performance work, and systems with visible trade-offs.</p>

          <table class="profile-table">
            <tbody>
              <tr><th scope="row">Current role</th><td>AI research at GREIA</td></tr>
              <tr><th scope="row">Study</th><td>MSc Informatics Engineering</td></tr>
              <tr><th scope="row">Languages</th><td>Python, C, C++</td></tr>
              <tr><th scope="row">Interests</th><td>ML, data science, cybersecurity</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <aside class="profile-illustration" aria-label="Illustrated Carles profile badge">
          <span aria-hidden="true">C</span>
          <strong>Carles</strong>
          <small>researcher · developer · music listener</small>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-grid" aria-label="Work and personal interests">
      <article class="window">
        <div class="window-title"><h2>Work &amp; research</h2><small>technical room</small></div>
        <div class="window-body reading">
          <p>My working zone is practical software and applied research. Current themes include music recommendation, formal explainability, and cybersecurity.</p>
          <p>I am contributing to the <a href="https://github.com/orgs/spotifai-tfg">SpotifAI</a> music recommendation project.</p>
          <a class="bevel-button green" href="/projects">Browse projects</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="window">
        <div class="window-title"><h2>Away from work</h2><small>personal room</small></div>
        <div class="window-body reading">
          <p>Music is the constant, which is why it keeps finding its way into technical projects. I also enjoy photography, space exploration, and supporting FC Barcelona.</p>
          <div class="button-row">
            <a class="bevel-button" href="/music">Enter music room</a>
            <a class="bevel-button" href="/links">Open links</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <aside class="sidebar-module contact-module">
      <div class="window-title"><h2>Contact &amp; profiles</h2></div>
      <div class="contact-body">
        <span class="status-line"><span class="status-dot live"></span><span>Public profiles available</span></span>
        <a href="https://github.com/carless7">GitHub ↗</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/carles-sanchez">LinkedIn ↗</a>
        <a href="https://greia.udl.cat/">GREIA ↗</a>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .profile-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 230px;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 18px 20px;
  }

  .profile-copy .intro {
    color: var(--water-deep);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .profile-table {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 16px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    border: 1px solid #a6d2e2;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .profile-table th,
  .profile-table td {
    padding: 6px 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #c9e5ef;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .profile-table th {
    width: 130px;
    color: var(--water-deep);
    background: #e0f5fb;
  }

  .profile-table tr:nth-child(even) td {
    background: #f1fbfe;
  }

  .profile-illustration {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    padding: 17px 12px;
    border: 1px solid #6eafc8;
    border-radius: 7px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e8fbff 0%, #bceefa 66%, #8bd26d 67%, #5eb04c 100%);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 #fff, 0 3px 7px rgba(0, 70, 100, 0.18);
  }

  .profile-illustration > span {
    display: grid;
    width: 112px;
    height: 112px;
    place-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: #fff;
    font: bold 50px/1 'Trebuchet MS', Verdana, sans-serif;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 2px var(--water-deep);
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 33% 25%, #fff 0 8%, rgba(255,255,255,.55) 9% 19%, transparent 20%), linear-gradient(145deg, var(--aqua), var(--water) 53%, var(--water-deep));
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 65, 95, 0.24), inset 0 -14px 22px rgba(0, 55, 100, 0.18);
  }

  .profile-illustration strong,
  .profile-illustration small {
    display: block;
  }

  .profile-illustration strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font: bold 18px/1.2 'Trebuchet MS', Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  .profile-illustration small {
    margin-top: 3px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 9px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .contact-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px 16px;
    padding: 9px 11px;
  }

  .contact-body .status-line {
    margin: 0 auto 0 0;
  }

  .contact-body > a {
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .profile-body,
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .profile-illustration {
      max-width: 260px;
    }

    .profile-table th {
      width: 105px;
    }

    .contact-body {
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
